# Cloudflare Workers Static Assets — custom response headers.
# https://developers.cloudflare.com/workers/static-assets/headers/
#
# The game's assets are unversioned (js/ui.js, css/style.css, …), so without
# this a browser can keep serving stale code after a deploy — exactly what made
# the iPad keep hitting an already-fixed bug. `no-cache` lets the browser store
# the file but forces it to revalidate against the edge on every load; Workers
# serves ETags, so unchanged files come back as a tiny 304 and changed files are
# fetched fresh. Players always run the latest deployed build, no manual cache
# clearing required.
/*
  Cache-Control: no-cache
